{"product_id":"organic-hand-wash-250ml","title":"Vielö Organic Hand Wash 250ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eNourishing organic hand wash, specially designed to cleanse gently while leaving the hands soft and smooth.\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eCreated with organic whey (nourishing), soy protein (strengthening) and organic extracts of lavender (soothing), nettle (antioxidant) and rosemary (stimulating).\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eSuitable for all skin types.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Shake well before use. Dispense into wet hands. Rinse thoroughly. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eLactis Serum Proteinum**, Aqua*, Glycerin**, Decyl Glucoside*, Disodium Cocoyl Glutamate*, Betaine*, Polyglyceryl-3 Caprate*, Xanthan Gum*, Sodium Cocoyl Glutamate*, Citric Acid*, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil**, Salvia Officinalis Oil**, Potassium Sorbate, Citronellol**\/***, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil**, Geraniol**\/***, Hydrolyzed Soy Protein*, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate*, Sodium Lactate*, Caesalpinia Spinosa Gum*, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Extract**, Urtica Dioica Leaf Extract**, Rosmarinus Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Sodium Benzoate.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e* from natural origin (99,8%)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e** certified organic (67,5%)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products. \u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49091863740743,"sku":null,"price":23.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-hand-wash-250ml-158204.jpg?v=1739897343","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/organic-hand-wash-250ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}